{"tid":1072744,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"為何通電話亦是罪名","createTime":"2019-03-22T08:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T16:36:18.000Z","uid":86723,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ccc4bcf023b1a89ed9125ac9b0dca91c60fa50","tid":1072744,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"經理 :<br />\n掉那媽 仆街響樹玩電話<br />\n連電話都快將爆炸<br />\n吳官都呵斥你痴筋啦<br />\n<br />\n撥個輪 千里索命不斷打<br />\n若接聽她會鳩叫呀<br />\n如不聽則比佢屌到化<br />\n<br />\n訴說那問題法團  就隔半分搵我一轉<br />\n你若說出不滿剩餘何元<br />\n是你心中一種格局大亂 才搭線搭八百幾轉<br />\n<br />\n阿婆：<br />\n為何通電話亦是罪名 為何port經理是件壞事情<br />\n<br />\n一陣作埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274a47baec85d2c3c7c20fcdb5803a33ae115d06","tid":1072744,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T08:10:53.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀:<br />\n<br />\n不斷打電話罪呢個罪名真係好好笑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1069906/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1069906/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"04f898832be34b787c5f2b7b34dc893e5b364899","tid":1072744,"uid":110876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:33:24.000Z","msg":"個話字好似唔太啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba27a2aefc89eec5448fef2e0e3b1f938766537d","tid":1072744,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04f898832be34b787c5f2b7b34dc893e5b364899","tid":1072744,"uid":110876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:33:24.000Z","msg":"個話字好似唔太啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:33:52.000Z","msg":"咩歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3632f4ada8a110e87d5bbaa21850d645e2370ba3","tid":1072744,"uid":148778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T15:51:12.000Z","msg":"句「為何通通電是件壞事情」冇咗？"},{"pid":"db7e1eb3b26e9ba26606ba97d1507a6e08646f12","tid":107